description:
backend/src/workers/generation.js exports createGenerationWorker() but server.js never imports or calls it. The BullMQ worker is never instantiated.

This means: routes queue jobs to the 'generation' queue, but no worker is listening to process them. All image/video generation will stay 'pending' forever.

Fix: In server.js, after plugins are registered, import and start the worker:
import { createGenerationWorker } from './workers/generation.js';
createGenerationWorker({ db: fastify.db, wsBroadcast: fastify.ws.broadcast, storagePath: config.storage.path });
